  "informal_statement": "For every natural n, four times the sum of the first n cubes equals (n(n+1))^2 (Nicomachus's theorem).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: peel the last cube with Finset.sum_range_succ, apply the hypothesis, and ring closes the quartic identity (k(k+1))^2 + 4(k+1)^3 = ((k+1)(k+2))^2.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_cubes (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), i ^ 3) * 4 = (n * (n + 1)) ^ 2",
